<?xml version='1.0' encoding='utf-8'?>

<introduction xml:id="AT-intro" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
    <paragraphs xml:id="AT-readiness">
    <title>Readiness Assurance</title>
    <p>
        Before beginning this chapter, you should be able to...
    </p>
    <ol marker="1.">
        <li>
            <p>State the definition of a spanning set, and determine if a set of Euclidean vectors spans <m>\IR^n</m>.</p>
            <ul>
                <li>
                    <p>Review: <xref ref="EV2"/></p>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </li>
        <li>
            <p>State the definition of linear independence, and determine if a set of Euclidean vectors is linearly dependent or independent.</p>
            <ul>
                <li>
                    <p>Review: <xref ref="EV4"/></p>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </li>
        <li>
            <p>
            State the definition of a basis, and determine if a set of Euclidean vectors is a basis.
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li>
                    <p>Review: <xref ref="EV5"/>,
                    <xref ref="EV6"/></p>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </li>
        <li>
            <p>Find a basis of the solution space to a homogeneous system
of linear equations.</p>
            <ul>
                <li>
                    <p>Review: <xref ref="EV7"/></p>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </li>
    </ol>
    </paragraphs>
</introduction>